  • public abstract class AbstractSortedNumericDocValues
extends org.apache.lucene.index.SortedNumericDocValues
    Base implementation that throws an IOException for the DocIdSetIterator APIs. This impl is safe to use for sorting and aggregations, which only use advanceExact(int) and SortedNumericDocValues.docValueCount() and SortedNumericDocValues.nextValue().
